The Sennheiser Momentum Wireless are a fantastic choice. They have a more straightforward function than the Parrot Zik (read: they don’t need an app to work), better sound than the Samsung Level On, and are built to last you a good long time. Yes, $500 is a lot of money, but for someone who needs an all-in-one headphone, and has the means, the Sennheiser Momentum Wireless may just be the best option currently available.
